description: Doggystyle Miami Hot Dogs is dishing out a mighty delicious twist on traditional Hot Dog dishes. With a gourmet take on tasty creations (including hot dogs, small bites, and desserts), Florida foodies just can’t stop craving this savory selection of high-quality dogs & toppings. For a bite of the best that Miami has to offer, come fetch yourself something good from this truck.
name: DoggyStyle Miami Hot Dogs
